p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‎‎Build the most overpowered, imbalanced killing machine, and <strong>break the game!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2441700/extras/acf0bd57b3efdf7f6ceb22681b03789c.poster.avif?t=1773842566\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2441700/extras/acf0bd57b3efdf7f6ceb22681b03789c.webm?t=1773842566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2441700/extras/acf0bd57b3efdf7f6ceb22681b03789c.mp4?t=1773842566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>💀 IT'S A DANGEROUS JUNGLE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This city's run by gangsters and psychos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hustle and deal with 40+ NPCs, hire hackers and saboteurs, get into street fights, steal, and sell people out.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You do what you need to do.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2441700/extras/24f3f81a34937789809c83eb0380a1c9.poster.avif?t=1773842566\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2441700/extras/24f3f81a34937789809c83eb0380a1c9.webm?t=1773842566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2441700/extras/24f3f81a34937789809c83eb0380a1c9.mp4?t=1773842566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🤜🤛 YOU AIN'T ALONE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Luckily, <strong>your little bruv King is in your corner - watching your back and calling things out</strong>. After all, you're doing this all for him. For a chance to get him into the city and save his life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‎‎</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‎</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‎‎‎‎‎</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So wassup?! You still reading?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step up and fight like a wild animal, smashing car sized pit bots that wanna kill you dead to the deafening roars of the blood thirsty crowds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step up to New Brakka - The Mech Fighting Capital of the World.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Step up to UNDERDOGS.</strong></p>",
